DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T1.Id, T1.GroupingId, T1.SpotLag, T1.FixedTenor, T6.value FixedDayCounter, T7.value FixedCalendar, T8.value FixedConvention, T9.value FixedPaymentConvention, T10.value IndexName, T1.OnTenor, T1.RateCutoff FROM ORE.dbo.ConventionsAverageOIS T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter T6 ON T1.FixedDayCounter = T6.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesCalendar T7 ON T1.FixedCalendar = T7.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention T8 ON T1.FixedConvention = T8.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention T9 ON T1.FixedPaymentConvention = T9.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T10 ON T1.IndexName = T10.value

field.name: *FixedDayCounter
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedDayCounter, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *FixedCalendar
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedCalendar, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesCalendar !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *FixedConvention
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedConvention,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *FixedPaymentConvention
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedPaymentConvention,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *IndexName
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value IndexName,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY value
